Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.76,0:02:42.43,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur6}胜负仅此一次
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.43,0:02:45.23,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur6}现在将其点燃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.56,0:02:52.82,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur6}焦躁不安  渴求着更多
