Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.61,0:02:58.99,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur6}感受这炽热
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.99,0:03:03.12,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur6}撩动感官  刺激的浪漫
